title: Sean Morris of Toprank Int. Veh. Importers
description:
Sean Morris has done a lot, from being in the Navy, to the crew chief of an R34 GT-R in World Challenge, to being the director of Toprank International Vehicle Importers, a company that brings in all those fun cars that Japan made that we couldn't get, until now. If you want to know about Skylines, Japanese cars, or importing, give this a listen. 

Check out his inventory here: https://www.importavehicle.com/vehicles

This show is also a video, with visual assets paired to the conversation: https://youtu.be/-3VQA2N9gC4

Follow us!

T: @thesmokingtire @zackklapman @tyndago

IG: @thesmokingtire @fakezackklapman 

 

Check out our merch!

https://teespring.com/stores/thesmokingtire?page=1
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
